    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Business Interpretation\n",
        "\n",
        "Credit History is one of the strongest predictors of loan approval.\n",
        "\n",
        "Applicants with higher income have a greater probability of loan approval.\n",
        "\n",
        "Loan amount and repayment term influence approval decisions.\n",
        "\n",
        "Using this model can help reduce manual effort and improve consistency in loan screening.\n",
        "\n",
        "A deployment threshold of 0.6 is recommended to reduce risky approvals while maintaining a reasonable approval rate."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Uj8_sLBNoMtO"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# Loan Approval Prediction\n",
        "\n",
        "## Objective\n",
        "Build a machine learning model to predict loan approval using applicant information.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Data Preprocessing\n",
        "- Handled missing values using mode and median imputation.\n",
        "- Encoded categorical variables using Label Encoding.\n",
        "- Scaled numerical features using StandardScaler.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Class Imbalance Handling\n",
        "- Applied SMOTE to balance the classes.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Models Evaluated\n",
        "1. Logistic Regression\n",
        "2. Random Forest\n",
        "\n",
        "## Conclusion\n",
        "Logistic Regression achieved the best ROC-AUC score and is recommended for deployment."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "GIUsddZAoU3K"
      }
    },
